{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act15d0_level_act15d0_st02","storyGroup":"act15d0","storySort":18,"storyDependence":"act15d0_level_act15d0_08_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"MB-ST-2","storyName":"正确的代价","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"越狱故事结束，缪尔赛思终于表露出了她的真实意图，赫默则选择了拒绝。最终，缪尔赛思留下忠告离开。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act15d0/level_act15d0_st02","avgTag":"幕间","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act15d0_st02","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":16,"characters":["缪尔赛思","赫默","梅尔","安东尼"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_ac15_3add.png","y":"-80","x":"-250","fadetime":"0","id":5},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.7","yScaleFrom":"1.7","xScaleTo":"1.6","yScaleTo":"1.6","duration":"3","block":"false","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nightoflongmen_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_nightoflongmen_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":8},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"斐尔迪南......能量科主任。","id":9},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......是的。","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"不过，比起这个，我更在意的是......","id":11},{"type":"dialog","id":12},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":13},{"type":"imagetween","xTo":"-320","yTo":"200","duration":"0.6","block":"true","id":14},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":15},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":16},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"为什么，塞雷娅，会，出现在，这里！","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"这个问题正是我想问你的，为什么塞雷娅会出现在这里，缪尔赛思主任？","id":18},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......这个问题是什么意思？","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"塞雷娅是你在这次事件中的帮手，不是吗？确切地说，原本是你的帮手。","id":20},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"哎呀，为什么你会这么想？","id":21},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"在谈话开始时，我就一直在想你在这件事情中所处的位置。","id":22},{"type":"dialog","id":23},{"type":"imagetween","xFrom":"-320","xTo":"200","yFrom":"200","yTo":"-150","duration":"1","block":"true","id":24},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我相信你与海德兄弟以及能量科无关，但如果你是了解事情经过的旁观者，那你找到我的行为就显得过于热情。","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"所以我的初步判断是，你在这件事情中应当是我的“竞争者”。","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你也想要安东尼来做些什么。","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"而在这件事情中，最让我感到不可思议的，就是塞雷娅的出现。","id":29},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"她已经完全与莱茵生命断绝了关系，现在的她唯一的身份是罗德岛的干员。","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"她应当没有任何理由插手这件事。","id":31},{"type":"dialog","id":32},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":33},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":34},{"type":"image","id":35},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":36},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":37},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":38},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":39},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#1","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"哎呀，这样说的话，我也可以说她是你的王牌呢。","id":41,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我确实不知道她居然真的在那个时间出现在了那里哦。","id":42,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我还记得你开始说的话——","id":44,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":45},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":46},{"type":"character","id":47},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":48},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"1","id":49},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":50},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":51},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0.8","keep":"true","id":52},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":54},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"2","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我所了解的，只有它的开端——","id":56,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"海德兄弟针对被关押在曼斯菲尔德监狱中，西蒙家族唯一的幸存者，安东尼·西蒙展开了一场蓄谋已久的刺杀。","id":57,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"还有它的结果——","id":58,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"以安东尼为首的几人团伙成功逃出了曼斯菲尔德监狱，并且与你们两个完成了汇合，目前已经离开了哥伦比亚。","id":59,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"中间具体发生了什么事，很遗憾，原本我有了解的机会，不过现在已经没有了。","id":60,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":61},{"type":"dialog","id":62},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":63},{"type":"character","id":64},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":65},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":66},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":67},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":68},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","amount":"0","keep":"true","id":69},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":70},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":71},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"1","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"假设你是我的“竞争者”，那么你不应该只了解这一点，你也应该有一个帮手，而这个帮手应该将能够告诉你监狱中发生的事情。","id":73,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但你没有，从种种迹象来看，我相信你是真的不知道这一连串发生的事情。","id":74,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"再联想到塞雷娅的突然出现。","id":75,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我只能得出一个结论，那就是——","id":76,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":77},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":78},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":79},{"type":"image","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/1b/Avg_avg_ac15_3add.png","fadetime":"0","id":80},{"type":"imagetween","xScaleFrom":"1.1","yScaleFrom":"1.1","xScaleTo":"1.05","yScaleTo":"1.05","duration":"5","block":"false","id":81},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":82},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":83},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"她原本是你的合作者，但她却违背了你们的协议。","id":84,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"但是既然如此，你们的出现也应当是个意外，为什么她会将安东尼交给你？","id":85,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"即使你们同样都和罗德岛有关系，但在这件事上如果真如你所说，她的立场应当完全与你对立，不是吗？","id":86,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......不。确实直到刚才，我也一直没有想明白，卡夫卡不可能是她的对手，理论上她应当才是最后的胜利者。","id":87,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"而我们......并没有什么联系，她实在没有理由将安东尼交给我。","id":88,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是现在我明白了。","id":89,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":90},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":91},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"image","id":93},{"type":"background","image":"https://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_bar_1.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":94},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#6","id":95},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":96},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":97},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#6","focus":"2","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......啊哈，原来如此，是为了骗过我吗。","id":99,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_char_249_muesys_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"1","id":100},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"没错。","id":101,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"接下来只是我的猜测。","id":102,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"1","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"对她来说，在掌握......不，我不是很想用这个词......","id":104,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"1","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"还是营救吧，在营救完安东尼后，她可以说是最后的赢家。","id":106,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"对她来说，安东尼最好的去处，并不是来到你的手上，因为那会助长你的势力，所以她会做的事应该是将安东尼截下，由她自己掌控。","id":107,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我不知道她在干什么，我也不想知道，但是她肯定知道海德兄弟不会就此善罢甘休，而她将要背叛的你也不会。","id":108,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#4","focus":"2","id":109},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"所以她利用了在整个事件中直到最后才登场这一点，将自己完全地从这件事情中从台面上隐去。","id":110,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"虽然我觉得她不会怕我和海德兄弟，不过，好吧，多一事不如少一事，是我我也会这么选。","id":111,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"2","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"而且，她在哥伦比亚应该确实还有事......算了，这和这件事应该无关。","id":113,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"1","id":114},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"她......算了，总之，我们的出现对她来说应当也是个意外，恐怕是她从卡夫卡那里大致了解了我们这边的情况后做出的判断吧。","id":115,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":116},{"type":"character","id":117},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":118},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#6","focus":"2","id":119},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......真是漂亮的推理，赫默小姐。","id":120,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_char_249_muesys_6.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你猜的一点都不错，正是我告诉塞雷娅这件事的。","id":121,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_char_249_muesys_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"2","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"杰斯顿在那之后应该是被发现并不是真正的狱卒而被收监了，导致我这边也没有收到有关他的情报。","id":123,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我确实被塞雷娅摆了一道。唉，虽然我一开始就觉得塞雷娅不会乖乖把人交给我就是了。","id":124,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"1","id":125},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......那你为什么还要找她帮忙？","id":126,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#4","focus":"2","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"那当然是因为——","id":128,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"没有办法啊。","id":130,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"公司内部我没有那么信得过又有能力做到这件事的人。","id":131,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"要是我有别的人可以依靠，我才不想麻烦塞雷娅呢。","id":132,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#2","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我虽然是生态科主任，不过其实是很弱小的哦。","id":134,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/33/Avg_char_249_muesys_2.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你看，我现在不仅人被她抢走了，还要惨兮兮地想办法看能不能把人给要回来，应该没有别的主任像我一样了吧。","id":135,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/33/Avg_char_249_muesys_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......所以，你来找我果然是想要我交出安东尼吗。","id":137,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":138},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":140},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$mist_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_mist_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","crossfade":"2","id":141,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#1","focus":"2","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"如果我说是的话，你会交吗？","id":143,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#1","focus":"1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"安东尼现在已经离开这里前往罗德岛了，即使我说可以也没有用。","id":145,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#1","focus":"2","id":146},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"放心，虽然我一开始确实是抱着这个想法，不过现在，我稍微改变了主意。","id":147,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"首先，如果我没猜错的话，罗德岛和这次事件没有任何关联，跟你来的人，只是受你雇佣护卫你来到哥伦比亚采购一些器材，没错吧？","id":148,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#1","focus":"1","id":149},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......没错，这是我的个人行为，我......欺骗了他们。","id":150,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#6","focus":"2","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你确实不擅长说谎呢，赫默小姐。","id":152,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_char_249_muesys_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"2","id":153},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"总之，我大概明白了。","id":154,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你的目的，应当也是让安东尼成为罗德岛的一员，或者至少被这家公司保护，这是你能够想到的最好的方法。","id":155,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"而塞雷娅虽然想要截走安东尼这条线索，但是对她来说，且不说安东尼愿不愿意配合她的臭脾气......","id":156,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"即使安东尼愿意，对塞雷娅来说，他恐怕也只是一个麻烦。","id":157,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"所以她选择让安东尼跟着你们加入罗德岛，这确实是一个不错的选择。","id":158,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"倒不如说，对她来说，恐怕安东尼只要能够完成越狱，并且我和斐尔迪南没有如意对她来说已经足够了。","id":159,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"而安东尼在越狱之后想做什么，能做什么，并不是她关注的重点。","id":160,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"是这样吗？","id":162,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_char_242_mayer-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"是哦，我是很难想象塞雷娅真的关心什么人的样子，其实一开始她会同意帮我我都觉得很奇怪了。","id":164,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"2","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"但是为什么加入罗德岛就好了？罗德岛不会有麻烦吗？","id":166,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_242_mayer-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"监狱的事情不会闹得很大，因为细查下去会把海德兄弟也拉出来，他们只会拼了命地掩盖这件事。","id":168,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"而罗德岛虽然和莱茵生命有合作关系，但是这件事只要没有来到台面上，那么就有很大的回转空间。","id":169,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"也就是说，安东尼如果成为罗德岛的一员的话，那么他反而暂时安全了。","id":170,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"虽然我也不清楚塞雷娅和罗德岛究竟建立了怎样的合作关系，但我多少了解过这家公司。","id":171,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我想如果我是那个罗德岛的首领，我不会介意接收安东尼。","id":172,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"2","id":173},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"诶，我都要被绕晕了......","id":174,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_242_mayer-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"1","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"简单来说呢，就是塞雷娅从我手上抢走了原本我希望她交给我的东西。","id":176,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"但她也没有就此据为己有，而是把它卖给了一家戒备森严的商店。","id":177,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","name2":"char_242_mayer#4","focus":"2","id":178},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"啊，这样我就听懂了。不过......所以呢？","id":179,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/33/Avg_char_242_mayer-5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":180},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"所以你希望目前在那家商店工作的我，能够和商店的主人交涉，将那样东西卖给你？","id":181,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":182},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"没错~","id":183,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"如果塞雷娅选择自己保下安东尼，我应该是暂时没有办法再做些什么的。","id":184,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"但是既然她选择了交给罗德岛，那么这件事就还有余地。","id":186,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"放心，我自然不会让你一个人去做这件事。","id":188,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"前防卫科主任塞雷娅可以和罗德岛达成合作关系，我生态科主任缪尔赛思自然也可以。","id":189,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我希望你做的是成为我和罗德岛之间沟通的桥梁。而作为回报，我会给你回到莱茵生命的机会。","id":190,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"甚至是一个挽回“炎魔”事件的机会。","id":192,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":194,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_242_mayer#1","id":195},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"......诶，听起来怎么感觉像是在做坏事一样。","id":196,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_242_mayer-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"不要误会，梅尔小姐，这是交易。","id":198,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#7","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"这片大地上的大部分事情都是没有那么温情脉脉的。","id":200,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"就好像罗德岛是因为在塞雷娅身上看到了价值才会庇护她。","id":201,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"就好像塞雷娅是认为你们可以安全护送安东尼回到罗德岛才会选择将他交给你们。","id":202,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"而我也相信，最终即使罗德岛接收了安东尼，也不会只是因为听说了他的过去而想要帮助他。","id":203,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我们可以赋予一些事情好的意义让它看起来不那么丑陋，但不能说这些事情本来就这么美好。","id":204,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"举个例子，我也可以说我现在在公司内势单力薄，然后尽力将总辖美化成一个出色的首领，以此来让你认为帮助我是“正确”的。","id":206,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"如果我这么做了，你绝不会发出刚才那样的感慨。","id":207,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"倒不如说，其实这才是我的长项哦？","id":209,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"而我没有这么做，是出于这场谈话下来对于赫默小姐的尊重。","id":211,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"出于这份尊重，我愿意给出对等，甚至在这之上的利益来交换安东尼这条线索，不知道你意下如何，赫默小姐？","id":212,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","name2":"char_242_mayer#1","focus":"2","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"赫默，怎么办？","id":214,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_242_mayer-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":216,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我......","id":217,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":218},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":219},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0","fadetime":"0.2","id":220},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#2","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我拒绝。","id":222,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_char_108_silent_1-2.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":223},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":224},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#3","focus":"2","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"哎呀，为什么？我觉得我给出的条件已经足够优渥了哦？","id":226,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_char_249_muesys_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#3","focus":"1","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"缪尔赛思主任，你似乎从头到尾都没有问过，我想要安东尼做什么。","id":228,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"是不是你下意识地以为，我也和你还有塞雷娅一样，都想要安东尼“这条线索”？","id":229,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#3","focus":"2","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"难道不是吗？","id":231,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_char_249_muesys_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#5","focus":"2","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我会用来作为制衡能量科的手段之一使用，塞雷娅虽然我还不清楚她的具体想法，但肯定有她的用途。","id":233,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"而你。","id":234,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你是一个因为实验失控而不得不离开莱茵生命的研究员，你想要用这条线索来向莱茵生命索取什么。","id":235,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#6","focus":"2","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"难道不是吗？","id":237,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_char_249_muesys_6.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":238},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......我并不打算使用“这条线索”，缪尔赛思主任。","id":240,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"如果塞雷娅最后没有出场，而安东尼依然通过某种方式获救，并且与我和梅尔汇合，我或许也会建议他加入罗德岛。","id":242,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但这并不是因为我想要通过罗德岛保管他“这条线索”。","id":243,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我们在这场谈话中，你用了许多次“这条线索”的说法，我并不喜欢这样的说法。","id":245,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"对我来说，安东尼并不是“一条线索”，而是一个活生生的人。","id":246,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"一整个家族一夜之间锒铛入狱，自己还不得不在监狱中忍受牢狱之灾的可怜的人！","id":247,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"如果有什么更好的去处，我会建议他，也会尽我所能地帮助他去。","id":248,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"而不是想着将他留在身边，作为未来的筹码。","id":249,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我认为这样是正确的。","id":250,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":251},{"type":"dialog","id":252},{"type":"character","id":253},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":254},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#4","focus":"2","id":255},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"看来，交涉决裂了呢。","id":256,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#4","focus":"1","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......很遗憾。","id":258,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"如果没有别的事，那么我们先走了。","id":259,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":260},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":261},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":262},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$calamity_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_calamity_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":263,"musicid":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":264},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#7","focus":"2","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"唉，你不会真的以为，让你听到了这么多的事情，我会轻易地放你离开吧，赫默研究员？","id":266,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#7","focus":"1","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不会。","id":268,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#1","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#7","focus":"1","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"所以我在去吃饭的时候，也做了一些准备。","id":270,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_char_108_silent_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#1","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#3","focus":"2","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"哦？","id":272,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_char_249_muesys_3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#2","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#3","focus":"1","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"安东尼！","id":274,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_char_108_silent_1-2.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":275},{"type":"character","id":276},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":277},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.2","fadetime":"0.5","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"......我在。","id":279},{"type":"delay","time":"0.51","id":280},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#7","fadetime":"1.5","id":281},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"1","id":282},{"type":"dialog","id":283},{"type":"delay","time":"4","id":284},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#3","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你......你不是已经离开哥伦比亚了吗？！","id":286,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/8/88/Avg_char_249_muesys_3.png"},{"type":"musicvolume","volume":"0.4","fadetime":"1","id":287},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_264_Mountain_1#7","focus":"1","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"离开的只是个幌子，安东尼还留在我们住的旅馆里，而我刚才把他叫了过来以防万一。","id":289,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"罗德岛的护卫建议我这么做，没想到在现在派上了用场。","id":290,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你不是想要安东尼吗？","id":291,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"现在是你唯一能够获得他的机会了，缪尔赛思主任。","id":292,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":293},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":294},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......要喝一杯吗，安东尼先生？","id":296,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","id":297},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"如果换一个场合，我会十分乐意与你一起喝一杯，缪尔赛思小姐。","id":298},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":299},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"真遗憾，那我们只好聊正事了。","id":300,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":301},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"那么，安东尼先生，你愿意跟我离开吗？","id":302,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#7","id":303},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"前提是你能够战胜我，这位小姐。","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"我旁听了一些你们的对话，不得不说，我并不讨厌你的思考方式。","id":305},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"以我来说，我也认为有些事并没有他们展现给别人的那么光鲜。","id":306},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"不过现在看来，这片大地上也确实还有一些真正美好的事物。","id":308},{"type":"dialog","id":309},{"type":"character","id":310},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":311},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","name2":"char_249_muesys_1#2","focus":"2","id":312},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"唉，看来我真的是被当做坏人了呢。","id":313,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/33/Avg_char_249_muesys_2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":314},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不，我说过，缪尔赛思主任。","id":315,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我不认为你是坏人。","id":316,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"站在你的立场上，你做了非常正确的事，我也认为你对我付出了足够多的善意。","id":317,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是，很遗憾，我无法认同你的想法，仅此而已。","id":318,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#4","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"......","id":320,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"总觉得好像不小心给自己树立了一个新的对手......","id":321,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/f/f7/Avg_char_249_muesys_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":322},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"你刚才也提到了制衡能量科，莱茵生命内部究竟发生了什么？","id":323,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"既然你拒绝与我交易，我当然就不能把这些告诉你啦。","id":325,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":326},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"不过如果你不打算就此收手的话，总有一天你也会知道的吧。","id":327,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","id":328},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我......","id":329,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":330},{"type":"delay","time":"0.7","id":331},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":332},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"总之，这一次我认输。","id":333,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"我可没有自信靠一个分身战胜安东尼这样的壮汉呢。","id":334,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#2","id":335},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"？！","id":336,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/a/a3/Avg_char_108_silent_1-2.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_242_mayer#2","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"分身？！","id":338,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_char_242_mayer-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#6","id":339},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"没错，这只是我的一个分身啦，是不是看起来还挺逼真的？","id":340,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_char_249_muesys_6.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":341},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"在离开之前，我要给你一个忠告，赫默研究员。","id":342,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你或许认为帮助安东尼是一件正确的事。","id":343,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#7","id":344},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"但事实并非如此。","id":345,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"在西蒙公司与海德兄弟的竞争中，如果说西蒙公司就是纯粹的被害者，那是可笑的。","id":346,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"双方都早有解决对方的打算，只是老史密斯棋差一着。","id":347,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......","id":349,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#7","id":350},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"也就是说，如果老史密斯抢在海德兄弟前动手，那么今天全家蹲在堡垒山城里的就不是西蒙一家，而是海德兄弟一家。","id":351,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"从这个角度来说，安东尼就真的只是一个受害者吗？","id":352,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/6/6e/Avg_char_249_muesys_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#3","id":353},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"但是......","id":354,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/7/79/Avg_char_108_silent_1-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":355},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"你觉得呢，安东尼？","id":356,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#7","id":357},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"我无法否认。","id":358},{"type":"dialog","id":359},{"type":"character","id":360},{"type":"stopmusic","time":"2","id":361},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":362},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#5","id":363},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"不过，这片大地上没有如果，我知道。","id":364,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"赫默研究员，我说这些是希望你能明白一点——","id":365,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"如果你想做正确的事，首先你要知道什么是正确的。其次，你要知道，并不是做正确的事就不需要付出代价。","id":366,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d2/Avg_char_249_muesys_5.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":367},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"......感谢你的忠告。","id":369,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_249_muesys_1#1","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"那么，再会。","id":371,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/5/53/Avg_char_249_muesys_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":372},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":373},{"type":"character","fadetime":"1","id":374},{"type":"playsound","key":"$b_char_defboost","volume":"0.7","id":375},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":376},{"type":"character","name":"char_242_mayer#1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"哇啊，变成一滩水了！？","id":378,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/4b/Avg_char_242_mayer-2.png"},{"type":"character","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"对了对了，安东尼的事情我会就此收手，不会再做什么多余的事。","id":380},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#4","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"居然能通过水说话......","id":382,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/c4/Avg_char_108_silent_1-4.png"},{"type":"character","id":383},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"说不定还会帮你们掩盖一些事情哦？感谢我吧。","id":384},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"既然我没有被当成坏人，就让我们下次有机会再聊吧。","id":385},{"type":"dialogue","name":"缪尔赛思","text":"安东尼先生，也祝你在罗德岛能够找到新的生活~","id":386},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","id":387},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"......感谢你的祝福，小姐。","id":388},{"type":"dialog","id":389},{"type":"character","id":390},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":391},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nightoflongmen_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta2_180603/m_dia_nightoflongmen_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":392,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","name2":"char_108_silent_1#1","focus":"1","id":393},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"那么，赫默小姐，这一次，我们应该真的出发了吧？","id":394},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","name2":"char_108_silent_1#1","focus":"2","id":395},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"嗯。","id":396,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_char_108_silent_1-1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":397},{"type":"character","id":398},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":399},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","id":400},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":401},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":402},{"type":"move","name":"left","ypos":"-70","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":403},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":404},{"type":"move","name":"left","ypos":"30","fadetime":"1.5","block":"true","id":405},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":406},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":407},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"梅尔，能不能扶我一下。","id":408,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_108_silent_1-5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"诶，怎么了？","id":410,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_char_242_mayer-3.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"我的双腿有些发软......","id":412,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_108_silent_1-5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"2","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"好哦。","id":414,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/4/47/Avg_char_242_mayer-3.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":415},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":416},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-150","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":417},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":418},{"type":"move","name":"left","ypos":"40","fadetime":"1.2","block":"true","id":419},{"type":"delay","time":"1.2","id":420},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":421},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"20","ystrength":"20","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":422},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"嘶......呼......","id":423,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_108_silent_1-5.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"不愧是主任级别的人物，我差一点就要被她压得说不出话来了。","id":425,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/d/d6/Avg_char_108_silent_1-5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","name2":"char_108_silent_1#5","focus":"1","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"在我看来，你的表现已经足够出色，赫默小姐。","id":427},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#5","name2":"char_242_mayer#4","focus":"2","id":428},{"type":"dialogue","name":"梅尔","text":"嗯，我也觉得，很帅呢。","id":429,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/3/33/Avg_char_242_mayer-5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_108_silent_1#1","name2":"char_242_mayer#2","focus":"1","id":430},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"谢谢。","id":431,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_char_108_silent_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","name2":"char_108_silent_1#1","focus":"1","id":432},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"我很好奇，罗德岛究竟是一个什么样的地方？","id":433},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","name2":"char_108_silent_1#1","focus":"2","id":434},{"type":"dialogue","name":"赫默","text":"从这里前往罗德岛的路很长，我会在路上慢慢为你说明。","id":435,"figure":"https://media.prts.wiki/c/ce/Avg_char_108_silent_1-1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_264_Mountain_1#11","id":436},{"type":"dialogue","name":"安东尼","text":"是吗，不错，我已经开始期待这一段旅途了。","id":437},{"type":"dialog","id":438},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"255","g":"255","b":"255","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":439},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"1","id":440},{"type":"character","id":441},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":442},{"type":"image","id":443}],"characters":["缪尔赛思","赫默","梅尔","安东尼"]}